title: St Peter Port North voters urged to register by midnight
text:
Residents who want to vote in the by-election for St Peter Port North have until midnight tonight to register.
A new Deputy will be elected following the death of Martin Storey earlier this year.
Candidates will be able to submit nominations between 26th October and 3rd November.
To find out how to register or for more information click here .
Last updated Thu 15 Oct 2015 Politics
